{"tid":764263,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]我啱啱試咗喺三藩市嗰間全機械整嘅漢堡包","createTime":"2018-08-01T21:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T23:29:10.000Z","uid":75232,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c5320b374f0486f0a671461503c04c6b357f556c","tid":764263,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T21:06:04.000Z","msg":"是咁的，六月尾嗰陣三藩市有間叫做Creator嘅漢堡包開始試業，一個禮拜剩係開兩日。到咗尋日，終於俾我買到飛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/045633_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F045633_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c1388715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/045655_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F045655_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=acadf8f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n間餐廳裝修好minimalistic.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/045757_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F045757_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e0e0290e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢部就係整包機，由右上開始鋸開個包，之後烘兩邊，落到下面就加醬，pickle, 蕃茄, 洋蔥, 生菜, 即磨車打芝士，最後就係塊扒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/050241_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F050241_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fd081e15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，塊扒煎到好熟囉...好乾...薯條同嘢飲因為係試業嘅關係所以免費！<br />\n<br />\n個包味道一般，我個人鍾意in-n-out多啲。<br />\n<br />\n至於價錢，六蚊美金即係47.1港紙，算係咁啦。"},{"pid":"315e1f172f5455d22cf2161b473252ce9d69a5e5","tid":764263,"uid":82717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T22:06:36.000Z","msg":"係幾平，但好少入城，有經過會試下。<br />\n除左In-N-Out, Habit burger grill  同都唔錯，有菜包(lettuce wrap)揀仲有free soda water 。"},{"pid":"89dd74294da9dbec8936ab392172302d08677ae7","tid":764263,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T22:15:19.000Z","msg":"下年會去三藩市<br />\n有冇地址？"},{"pid":"3973e51eb0ef9dc8c3b060413e56e7d042d410f0","tid":764263,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89dd74294da9dbec8936ab392172302d08677ae7","tid":764263,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T22:15:19.000Z","msg":"下年會去三藩市<br />\n有冇地址？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T22:19:57.000Z","msg":"680 Folsom Street, San Francisco, CA 94107<br />\n<br />\n不過而家都仲要上佢個網<a href=\"http://creator.rest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcreator.rest&d=iaCHxBfwVEno7mE5ptD2yBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=3107ac4d\" target=\"_blank\">http://creator.rest</a>買飛，唔係嘅話無得walk-in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f1733825b7d898ae6be195fc4de6abcb249b3d","tid":764263,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T22:21:31.000Z","msg":"有漢堡包自動販賣機就正"},{"pid":"cc3a0cd6fe89b6c11ef96c0141c5e6b6d53a5333","tid":764263,"uid":172365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T23:00:32.000Z","msg":"in-n-out 真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到宜家仲記得佢個芝士薯條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1543141fa187742f2de3f44ee3104210fce549","tid":764263,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3973e51eb0ef9dc8c3b060413e56e7d042d410f0","tid":764263,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89dd74294da9dbec8936ab392172302d08677ae7","tid":764263,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T22:15:19.000Z","msg":"下年會去三藩市<br />\n有冇地址？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T22:19:5